OL,3,CBritish Airways ranked among worst
OL,4,Cairlines for passenger satisfaction
OL,6,FBritish Airways has been ranked among
OL,7,Fthe worst airlines in a UK passenger
OL,8,Fsatisfaction survey.
OL,10,FThe airline's customer score for long-
OL,11,Fhaul flights was the joint third
OL,12,Flowest out of 17 carriers analysed by
OL,13,Fconsumer group Which?, at 59%.
OL,15,FIt received just two stars out of five
OL,16,Ffor boarding experience and value for
OL,17,Fmoney, and achieved three stars for
OL,18,Fthe other six categories assessed.
