OL,3,CBritish Airways ranked among worst
OL,4,Cairlines for passenger satisfaction
OL,6,FFor short-haul flights, British
OL,7,FAirways' score was 56%, which was the
OL,8,Ffifth lowest among 22 airlines.
OL,10,FThe company said it was hit by
OL,11,F"several factors outside of our
OL,12,Fcontrol" in 2023, such as strikes by
OL,13,Fair traffic controllers.
OL,15,FThe survey of Which? members was
OL,16,Fconducted in October last year and
OL,17,Frelates to more than 10,000 flights.
OL,19,FCustomer scores were based on overall
OL,20,Fsatisfaction and the likelihood to
OL,21,Frecommend.
