OL,3,CBritish Airways ranked among worst
OL,4,Cairlines for passenger satisfaction
OL,6,FThe best airlines for long and short-
OL,7,Fhaul flights were Singapore Airlines
OL,8,F(83%) and Jet2.com (81%) respectively.
OL,10,FAt the other end of the scale, the
OL,11,Fworst performers in the long-haul
OL,12,Franking were Lufthansa (56%), Air
OL,13,FCanada (58%), American Airlines (59%)
OL,14,Fand British Airways.
OL,16,FWizz Air (44%) was ranked bottom for
OL,17,Fshort-haul flights for the second year
OL,18,Fin a row.
OL,20,FIt was followed by Ryanair (47%),
OL,21,FIberia (49%) and Vueling (53%).
