OL,4,Cairlines for passenger satisfaction
OL,6,FWhich? said the standard of service
OL,7,Fexperienced by passengers last year
OL,8,Foften "fell well short of the mark",
OL,9,Fwith many people struggling to get
OL,10,Fsupport when needed.
OL,12,FThe sight of passengers being
OL,13,F"abandoned" in airport terminals when
OL,14,Fflights are delayed or cancelled "has
OL,15,Fbecome all too common", it added.
OL,17,FUK air fares reached record highs in
OL,18,F2023.
