OL,6,FRory Boland, editor of magazine Which?
OL,7,FTravel, said: "Air fares have soared
OL,8,Fin recent years, and the bare minimum
OL,9,Fpassengers should expect in return for
OL,10,Ftheir hard-earned cash is a reliable
OL,11,Fservice, with friendly, easy to access
OL,12,Fcustomer support when they are let
OL,13,Fdown.
