OL,6,F"While the likes of Jet2 continue to
OL,7,Fexcel in this regard, our survey shows
OL,8,Fthat passengers of many airlines are
OL,9,Fsadly being shortchanged ` with high
OL,10,Frates of last minute cancellations,
OL,11,Fabysmal customer service and sneaky
OL,12,Fextra fees for luggage hiking up the
OL,13,Ffinal price."
